---
 CMakeLists.txt                                      | 13 ++++++++++---
 contrib/ecalhdf5/CMakeLists.txt                     |  5 +++++
 contrib/ecalproto/CMakeLists.txt                    |  5 +++++
 ecal/core/CMakeLists.txt                            | 12 ++++++++----
 thirdparty/cmake_functions/CMakeLists.txt           |  2 ++
 .../cmake/CMakeFunctionsConfig.cmake.in             |  2 +-
